{"tid":1632182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可以比意見，但永不割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:22:32.000Z","uid":151966,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e87f0cb6a22ab35c6615ea4357d5dcdffbb32898","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:08.000Z","msg":"有見連登好多post和理非同勇武互屌<br />\n請大家記住，呢個運動係和理非加勇武一齊發功先可以發展到今時今日<br />\n大家一家人坐埋同一條船，冇左邊個都唔得<br />\n唔同人理念唔同，可以唔認同其他人ge行動比意見大家一齊改進<br />\n但係，我地絕對唔會割蓆，互屌分化<br />\n記住，我地只有彼此，只有信任彼此，先有一絲機會成功<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ee73464003a4bf9384180a14a3dd72bd3e1a9e","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f17091417e9f9d2a60e66c275651d2a97b8d2f7e","tid":1632182,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 10.7 爆食日 攪珠結果出爐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632126</a>"},{"pid":"76cc1e770155261da7edd8b5912318eef00d7fe3","tid":1632182,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"4a49f4285b277d7d05d9c7fac39f388c9c2f21e9","tid":1632182,"uid":233745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c9ff48d4167843c1e0d2e815c7cd39512e9f8f98","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a18729ba8cbd6e8249c18f9b6d981b3e48a78a5","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4dcf68c9b73024e6cbf4ef008562c28afa1703a","tid":1632182,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！ 而家只係要你入黎推post</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ef5798dbba0196884d513d4a206072df9a540c5","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b64ff78774111f15634ae655dcb5c7684200eb2a","tid":1632182,"uid":295190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"唔割<br />\n只係每次都可以繼續進步"},{"pid":"1af4b2ed848164de279430152995a49d84d1a0a1","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64ff78774111f15634ae655dcb5c7684200eb2a","tid":1632182,"uid":295190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"唔割<br />\n只係每次都可以繼續進步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"sofucking true槍口對外"},{"pid":"e9ed93d2cd327e548582eeaffb9231ba9dc49afe","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc91b5572e078b2fd4ab418f6e709a30953a34ea","tid":1632182,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:44.000Z","msg":"係俾意見，唔係屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ed65c36647ea8e405c6e2d0021c169e3caceb4","tid":1632182,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fa03737bcdb98126c68a4af7250ac9f87912957","tid":1632182,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"18區歌聲歡迎人權法"}]}